{"word":"G263 - ἀμάραντος - amárantos - am-ar'-an-tos - That fadeth not away","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀμάραντος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>amárantos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>am-ar'-an-tos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>That fadeth not away"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வாடாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"not fading away, unfading, perennial"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G3133 - μαραίνω - maraínō - mar-ah'-ee-no/3133\">G3133</a>; <i>unfading</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>perpetual:</i> - that fadeth not away."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}